videos.description: Tulsa QB Luke Skipper has his pass intercepted by Temple's Ty Mason who returns it 36 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Temple gets early pick-6

videos.description: Tulsa's Corey Taylor II runs in a three-yard touchdown to even the score at 7-7.
videos.headline: Taylor drives in 3-yard score

videos.description: Anthony Russo connects with Randle Jones on a 41-yard gain and later tucks it and runs for a 1-yard touchdown and a Temple lead.
videos.headline: Russo punches in 1-yard TD

videos.description: Ryquell Armstead finds a huge hole, cuts and bursts for a 22-yard touchdown run to extend Temple's lead.
videos.headline: Armstead bursts for 22-yard TD

videos.description: Tulsa QB Luke Skipper is stripped and sacked by DE Quincy Roche who recovers the fumble and scores a 50-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: DE takes strip sack 50 yards for TD

videos.description: Down 28-10 early in the fourth,  Cooper Edmiston intercepts Temple QB Anthony Russo to begin a Tulsa scoring drive.
videos.headline: Tulsa' INT sets up TD drive

videos.description: Tulsa's Corey Taylor II runs in a five-yard touchdown to shrink Tulsa's deficit to 28-17.
videos.headline: Taylor brings in 2nd TD
